      <title>markdown语法速查</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/15/markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E9%80%9F%E6%9F%A5/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/15/markdown%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E9%80%9F%E6%9F%A5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MarkDowd-基本语法"><a href="#MarkDowd-基本语法" class="headerlink" title="MarkDowd 基本语法"></a>MarkDowd 基本语法</h1><p>这些是 John Gruber 的原始设计文档中列出的元素。所有 Markdown 应用程序都支持这些元素</p><h2 id="标题（Heading）"><a href="#标题（Heading）" class="headerlink" title="标题（Heading）"></a>标题（Heading）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># H1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## H2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### H3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="粗体（Bold）"><a href="#粗体（Bold）" class="headerlink" title="粗体（Bold）"></a>粗体（Bold）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">**bold text**</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="斜体（Italic）"><a href="#斜体（Italic）" class="headerlink" title="斜体（Italic）"></a>斜体（Italic）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*italicized text*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="引用块（Blockquote）"><a href="#引用块（Blockquote）" class="headerlink" title="引用块（Blockquote）"></a>引用块（Blockquote）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; blockquote</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="有序列表（Ordered-List）"><a href="#有序列表（Ordered-List）" class="headerlink" title="有序列表（Ordered List）"></a>有序列表（Ordered List）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> First item</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> Second item</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">3.</span> Third item</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="无序列表（Unordered-List）"><a href="#无序列表（Unordered-List）" class="headerlink" title="无序列表（Unordered List）"></a>无序列表（Unordered List）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> First item</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> Second item</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> Third item</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="代码（Code）"><a href="#代码（Code）" class="headerlink" title="代码（Code）"></a>代码（Code）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="code">`code`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="分隔线（Horizontal-Rule）"><a href="#分隔线（Horizontal-Rule）" class="headerlink" title="分隔线（Horizontal Rule）"></a>分隔线（Horizontal Rule）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="链接（Link）"><a href="#链接（Link）" class="headerlink" title="链接（Link）"></a>链接（Link）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">title</span>](<span class="link">https://www.example.com</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="图片（Image）"><a href="#图片（Image）" class="headerlink" title="图片（Image）"></a>图片（Image）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt text</span>](<span class="link">image.jpg</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
